# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:8
translate chinese u19a2s6a_82d89999:

    # "I choose a path and walk towards where I feel the voice of Mi-Cha pulling me."
    "我选了一条路，朝着感觉米查的声音在召唤我的方向走去。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:28
translate chinese u19a2s6a_2499204d:

    # "The path leads into a sparse forest, with an overgrown trail winding through the trees."
    "这条路通向一片稀疏的森林，一条杂草丛生的小径在树林间蜿蜒盘旋。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:29
translate chinese u19a2s6a_cfc5fb48:

    # "I can hear a stream flowing nearby and a soft voice singing a pretty melody."
    "我听见附近有溪水流淌，还有柔和的歌声在哼唱着动人的旋律。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:36
translate chinese u19a2s6a_b3064858:

    # "I come around a corner and get a clear view of the stream and see Mi-Cha dancing in it."
    "我绕过一个弯，溪流尽收眼底，只见米查正在水中翩然起舞。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:37
translate chinese u19a2s6a_2d65b5e2:

    # "She spins and twirls in the water, streams of liquid rising up to follow her movements."
    "她在水中旋转飞舞，水流随她的动作翻涌而上。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:38
translate chinese u19a2s6a_ac786856:

    # "She seems oblivious to the world around her, lost in her own dance, moving to music that only she can hear."
    "她似乎对周遭的世界浑然不觉，沉浸在自己的舞蹈中，随着只有她能听见的乐声起舞。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:41
translate chinese u19a2s6a_d95000f9:

    # "Then I spot a figure, creeping in from the treeline. Another fucking bandit!"
    "这时我瞥见一个身影，正从树林边缘悄悄潜入。又是该死的强盗！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:42
translate chinese u19a2s6a_0ccb4fef:

    # "His sword is out and it's obvious what he has on his mind."
    "他已拔出长剑，意图昭然若揭。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:43
translate chinese u19a2s6a_a6d43ea4:

    # pc "Not today, asshole."
    pc "今天可没那么好过，混蛋。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:47
translate chinese u19a2s6a_7f78a502:

    # sst "Want some help? I'm feeling hungry."
    sst "要帮忙吗？我正饿着呢。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:49
translate chinese u19a2s6a_c84ba3e1:

    # sg "Want me to distract him while you crack his skull?"
    sg "要我吸引他的注意，让你给他一记闷棍？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:51
translate chinese u19a2s6a_4f156f03:

    # rb "Want some help? I'll clobber him."
    rb "要帮忙吗？我来揍他一顿。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:53
translate chinese u19a2s6a_cbe2391c:

    # gg "Want some help?"
    gg "要帮忙吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:55
translate chinese u19a2s6a_a9f2fb28:

    # bn "Do you need any help?"
    bn "你需要帮忙吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:57
translate chinese u19a2s6a_1a227f85:

    # cw "Want some help?"
    cw "需要帮忙吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:59
translate chinese u19a2s6a_16434dde:

    # pc "Nah, I got this."
    pc "不用，我搞定。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:60
translate chinese u19a2s6a_9a39bc02:

    # "I pick up a large rock and start sneaking towards the man."
    "我捡起一块大石头，开始悄悄向那人靠近。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:63
translate chinese u19a2s6a_564610ac:

    # mc "AAH!"
    mc "啊！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:64
translate chinese u19a2s6a_a48fac56:

    # "Bandit" "Hello girlie... you awful pretty to be out here in the woods all alone."
    "Bandit" "嗨，小妞……你一个人在这片树林里，真是美得吓人啊。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:65
translate chinese u19a2s6a_a4733775:

    # pc "She's not alone."
    pc "她不是一个人。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:68
translate chinese u19a2s6a_69fc93d3:

    # "He doesn't have time to react before I bring the rock down on top of his head and he crumples to the ground."
    "还没等他反应过来，我就把石头砸在他头上，他应声倒地。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:69
translate chinese u19a2s6a_564610ac_1:

    # mc "AAH!"
    mc "啊！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:72
translate chinese u19a2s6a_f661c820:

    # mc "Don't look! I didn't think anybody else was out here!"
    mc "别看！ 我以为这里没有别人！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:73
translate chinese u19a2s6a_0f1045ec:

    # pc "I'm sorry Mi-Cha, I didn't mean to scare you. I'm just trying to help."
    pc "对不起，米查，我不是故意吓你的。我只是想帮忙。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:74
translate chinese u19a2s6a_f4665b14:

    # mc "How do you know my name?"
    mc "你怎么知道我的名字？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:77
translate chinese u19a2s6a_5adb239d:

    # pc "It's a long story. Get dressed and I'll tell you all about it."
    pc "说来话长。你先穿上衣服，我再把一切都告诉你。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:96
translate chinese u19a2s6a_a6aec774:

    # "She puts some clothes on and I explain to her everything about coming from the other universe, about the bracelet, and the Ice Queen."
    "她穿好衣服后，我向她解释了一切：关于我来自另一个宇宙的事，关于手镯，还有关于冰雪女王。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:97
translate chinese u19a2s6a_a8ed1756:

    # mc "It is all very confusing."
    mc "这一切都让人很困惑。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:98
translate chinese u19a2s6a_23a9c589:

    # pc "I know. It's hard to believe, but it's all true, I promise."
    pc "我知道。虽然很难相信，但这一切都是真的，我向你保证。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:101
translate chinese u19a2s6a_834b46dc:

    # mc "I believe you. You are an honest man."
    mc "我相信你。你是个诚实的人。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:102
translate chinese u19a2s6a_f8a50858:

    # mc "And you saved my life."
    mc "而且你救了我的命。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:103
translate chinese u19a2s6a_7da4f896:

    # mc "I am yours now."
    mc "我现在属于你了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:104
translate chinese u19a2s6a_863b60e1:

    # pc "No, that's not necessary. I don't want that."
    pc "不，没必要。我不想那样。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:107
translate chinese u19a2s6a_a570e044:

    # mc "You do not want me?"
    mc "你不想要我？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:108
translate chinese u19a2s6a_62d20d40:

    # pc "No, I mean, I don't want you to be my property or anything. I want you to do what you want."
    pc "不，我是说，我不希望你成为我的财产之类的。我希望你做你想做的事。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:111
translate chinese u19a2s6a_03e0174a:

    # mc "I wish to travel with you and help you."
    mc "我想和你一起旅行，帮你做点事。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:112
translate chinese u19a2s6a_212ce784:

    # mc "I can do things. I am not as helpless as I seem."
    mc "我挺能干的。我并没有看起来那么无助。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:113
translate chinese u19a2s6a_0899dab2:

    # pc "I have no doubt. I'd love to have you along."
    pc "我毫不怀疑。我很乐意有你同行。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:134
translate chinese u19a2s6a_d2cb5253:

    # "With that, Mi-Cha gathers her supplies and we continue down the path to the north."
    "说完，米查收拾好行装，我们继续沿着小路向北走去。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:136
translate chinese u19a2s6a_7d0974c3:

    # sst "Hi Mi-Cha. I'm Nora."
    sst "嗨，米查。我是诺拉。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:137
translate chinese u19a2s6a_b3f3e6a0:

    # sst "I really like what you were doing back there with the water."
    sst "我真的很喜欢你刚才在水边做的那件事。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:138
translate chinese u19a2s6a_d47d2db0:

    # sst "I'm a mermaid, by the way. Normally I have a tail."
    sst "顺便说一下，我是美人鱼。平时我有条尾巴。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:139
translate chinese u19a2s6a_2864f3b6:

    # mc "Oh, wow. You must dance in the water beautifully."
    mc "哦，哇。你在水里跳舞一定很美。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:140
translate chinese u19a2s6a_8ae8974a:

    # mc "We should dance together some time."
    mc "我们改天一起跳舞吧。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:141
translate chinese u19a2s6a_e8bb2add:

    # sst "That could be fun."
    sst "那应该会很有趣。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:143
translate chinese u19a2s6a_5ff22eca:

    # rb "Hi Mi-Cha. My name's Reba."
    rb "嗨，米查。我叫蕾芭。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:144
translate chinese u19a2s6a_6f2fc345:

    # rb "You don't have a weapon or anything? What if you get attacked by a bunch of men or something?"
    rb "你没有武器之类的吗？万一被一群男人袭击怎么办？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:145
translate chinese u19a2s6a_c099b4f5:

    # mc "I have other ways of dealing with men, aside from hitting them."
    mc "除了打他们，我还有其他对付男人的办法。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:146
translate chinese u19a2s6a_cb2cf90f:

    # rb "Hm. I prefer hitting them."
    rb "嗯。我还是喜欢打他们。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:148
translate chinese u19a2s6a_5bc5d25b:

    # cw "Hi Mi-Cha. I'm Dana, by the way."
    cw "嗨，米查。顺便说一下，我是达娜。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:149
translate chinese u19a2s6a_29972c03:

    # cw "Your dance was beautiful back there... I'd love to see more of it sometime."
    cw "刚才你的舞跳得真美……真希望以后还能再看。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:150
translate chinese u19a2s6a_94b89eb1:

    # mc "Thank you. I'm sure we will get the opportunity. I'd love to see you dance too."
    mc "谢谢。我相信我们会有机会的。我也想看看你跳舞。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:151
translate chinese u19a2s6a_efd84ba8:

    # cw "Oh, um... I'm not much of a dancer."
    cw "哦，那个……我跳得不太好。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:152
translate chinese u19a2s6a_d1bcb6ee:

    # mc "You should though. I'll show you how."
    mc "你应该试试。我来教你。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:153
translate chinese u19a2s6a_80478591:

    # cw "Okay."
    cw "好。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:155
translate chinese u19a2s6a_ffe30799:

    # gg "I'm Adrian. Nice to meet you, Mi-Cha."
    gg "我是阿德里安。很高兴认识你，米查。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:156
translate chinese u19a2s6a_6a0b3d28:

    # mc "Nice to meet you as well."
    mc "我也一样。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:157
translate chinese u19a2s6a_4e33f4bf:

    # gg "Where did you learn to dance like that?"
    gg "你在哪里学的这种舞步？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:158
translate chinese u19a2s6a_3c8516f8:

    # mc "I have been training for it my whole life."
    mc "我这一辈子都在为此训练。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:159
translate chinese u19a2s6a_de0ec949:

    # mc "It's the thing I love to do the most."
    mc "这是我最喜欢做的事。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:160
translate chinese u19a2s6a_dbfaf680:

    # gg "I can't wait to see more of it."
    gg "我迫不及待想看更多了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:162
translate chinese u19a2s6a_0f3c13f7:

    # sg "Nice to meet you! I'm Kendra."
    sg "很高兴认识你！我是肯德拉。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:163
translate chinese u19a2s6a_6a0b3d28_1:

    # mc "Nice to meet you as well."
    mc "我也一样。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:164
translate chinese u19a2s6a_ff3814dc:

    # sg "Your dancing was so pretty! I want to see more!"
    sg "你的舞跳得真美！我还想看更多！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:165
translate chinese u19a2s6a_b3d79b50:

    # mc "Thank you. I'm sure you dance very pretty as well."
    mc "谢谢。我相信你跳舞也一定很美。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:166
translate chinese u19a2s6a_6bbdb960:

    # sg "I dance, but not like that. Yours is all swirl-woosh-glide and I'm all bow-chicka-wow-wow."
    sg "我会跳舞，但不是那种风格。你的舞步全是旋转、飞掠、滑行，而我的全是“噗嗤哇哇”。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:167
translate chinese u19a2s6a_d11b0a37:

    # mc "I don't know what that means, but I do believe that everybody should dance in whatever way feels good to them."
    mc "虽然我不明白那是什么意思，但我相信每个人都应该以自己觉得舒服的方式跳舞。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:168
translate chinese u19a2s6a_1a1c3141:

    # sg "Heck yeah!"
    sg "太对啦！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:170
translate chinese u19a2s6a_7b246276:

    # bn "I'm Juliana. Nice to meet you, Mi-Cha."
    bn "我叫朱莉安娜。很高兴认识你，米查。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:171
translate chinese u19a2s6a_6a0b3d28_2:

    # mc "Nice to meet you as well."
    mc "我也非常高兴认识你。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:172
translate chinese u19a2s6a_f68e579c:

    # bn "Where did you learn to dance like that?"
    bn "你在哪里学会这样跳舞的？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:173
translate chinese u19a2s6a_3c8516f8_1:

    # mc "I have been training for it my whole life."
    mc "我这一辈子都在为此训练。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:174
translate chinese u19a2s6a_de0ec949_1:

    # mc "It's the thing I love to do the most."
    mc "这是我最喜欢做的事。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6a.rpy:175
translate chinese u19a2s6a_55e12629:

    # bn "I've read about dancers like you, but never witnessed something like that. It's very fascinating."
    bn "我读过关于像你这样的舞者的报道，但从未亲眼见过。这太迷人了。"

